{"tid":2057031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍C-40A運輸機飛越台灣領空","createTime":"2020-06-09T06:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T10:51:55.000Z","uid":95138,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"659ecc9dccf0cafd74aa788402c693e8848e0063","tid":2057031,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:01:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006095002.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202006095002.aspx&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f5a624c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006095002.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n根據追蹤飛機動態的推特帳號Golf9和網站AirNav資訊，美軍1架C-40A「快船」運輸機今天上午從日本沖繩起飛，罕見自基隆航向台灣西海岸，穿越台灣領空，並自台南外海離去。<br />\n<br />\n美軍C-40運輸機是波音737-700的軍用版。<br />\n<br />\n對於美軍機動態，國防部發言人史順文少將指出，台海周邊海、空域狀況，國防部都能充分掌握，目前狀況均正常。"},{"pid":"45db31b58c174b97700444b60f76336621e25e83","tid":2057031,"uid":95138,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GO3iaWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGO3iaWQ.jpg&h=12835197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍1架C-40A「快船」運輸機9日上午從日本沖繩起飛，罕見自基隆穿越台灣領空，從台南外海離去。圖為美軍C-40運輸機從沖繩美軍嘉手納空軍基地起飛的檔案照片。中央社記者郭無患攝 109年6月9日"},{"pid":"9d25f0e8d3445963577b05b403a23fc7132bbe7e","tid":2057031,"uid":154486,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"唔想燈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc5b988246ad02a6be60967e2b2e0ff0d1e38a2","tid":2057031,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"係咪掟左D野落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65f4804aa304ac1829227ff7caf2cd4756742e6","tid":2057031,"uid":11454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"RTHK<br />\n<br />\n台灣軍方稱解放軍多架戰機短暫進入台灣空域<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，防衞部門表示，上午偵測到解放軍多架蘇30戰機，短暫進入台灣西南空域，台軍負責偵察和巡邏的戰機，全程掌握解放軍戰機飛行，並用廣播進行警告，採取「驅離」措施。台灣軍方強調，充分掌握台海周邊海、空域狀況，並積極應對，確維台灣安全。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-09 13:47:21"},{"pid":"20a914ec74c565a379c92a54ec0acbfa7bd1f46d","tid":2057031,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"支那嬲豬未"},{"pid":"b407a8520f25dc0d119ef1bf8cca0e45cb6eb47a","tid":2057031,"uid":261796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"efc5b988246ad02a6be60967e2b2e0ff0d1e38a2","tid":2057031,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"係咪掟左D野落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"掟左D槍落去"},{"pid":"53fc53a79afb3ae8f607ba38b39db8ec6f16cf24","tid":2057031,"uid":118882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Sir this way!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"97e6e7ffab6f10a27f8e7067f5d2f70c8bf95cfb","tid":2057031,"uid":128213,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9d25f0e8d3445963577b05b403a23fc7132bbe7e","tid":2057031,"uid":154486,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"唔想燈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"你見英國都吹風想承認台灣就個<br />\n台灣的存在 = 為世界帶來和平"},{"pid":"fa8a4e7aaf40e10fd9c7d16534e5e85f73bc6c4f","tid":2057031,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"進入中國領空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰狼出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc9b139d81f0a777de56e5617a31f40f858ee7f","tid":2057031,"uid":95138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":